# Website Redesign: Bento Grid & Modern Flat Design

Transition the current digital marketing affiliate hub to a modern, high-density Bento Grid layout with a focus on modular discovery and professional "product-as-app" aesthetics.

## Proposed Changes

### Core Design System

#### [MODIFY] [tailwind.config.js](file:///c:/Users/llmde/Desktop/app/tailwind.config.js)
- Update color palette to include:
  - Background: `#F3F4F6` (Canvas)
  - Primary: `#FF4F00` (International Orange)
  - Secondary: Slate gray for borders
  - Commission: `#00C853` (Vivid Green)
  - Surfaces: `#FFFFFF` (White cards)
- Remove rounded corners (sharp corners as per prompt).
- Remove shadows.

#### [MODIFY] [index.css](file:///c:/Users/llmde/Desktop/app/src/index.css)
- Implement global base styles for the new theme.
- Define `.bento-card` utility for modular tiles.
- Update typography to Inter (body) and technical heavy Sans-Serif (headings).

### Components

#### [MODIFY] [ProductCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/llmde/Desktop/app/src/components/ui/custom/ProductCard.tsx)
- Implement the "Refined product card" design:
  - 1px border, white background, sharp corners.
  - Hover effect: border-color change and subtle translateY.
  - Commission badge in vivid green.
  - Rectangular "Promote Now" button in Navy Blue.

#### [NEW] [BentoHero.tsx](file:///c:/Users/llmde/Desktop/app/src/sections/BentoHero.tsx)
- Create the main Bento Grid container using CSS Grid.
- Components to include:
  - **Hero Tile**: Large featured product highlight.
  - **Categories Tile**: Interactive grid of categories.
  - **Affiliate Stats Tile**: Real-time stats dashboard style.
  - **Search Command Bar**: Width-expanding filter/search bar.

### Search & Navigation Enhancements

#### [MODIFY] [BentoHero.tsx](file:///c:/Users/llmde/Desktop/app/src/sections/BentoHero.tsx)
- Remove the search command bar from the Bento grid.
- Adjust grid layout to fill the resulting space.

